{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
    <title>Austin Pocus - My personal site - About me</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
{% endblock %}

{% block main %}
<div class="home">
    <div class="sections">        
        <section class="main-section">
            <div class="pictures">
                <figure class="left">
                    <img class="picture" src="/img/me_and_sissy.jpg">
                    <figcaption>Me with my sister, Sara</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="right">
                    <img class="picture" src="/img/me.jpg">
                    <figcaption>Me, with more hair</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="heading">Bio</h2>

                <p>I've had a lifelong obsession with making things using computers. I started because I was a video game fanatic as a kid, and wanted to make my own games.</p>

                <p>Nearly 2 decades later, I still haven't built a game -- most of my experience has been on the web, but not just websites. I've also:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>Analyzed the sound waves from my guitar</li>
                    <li>Helped build industrial automation systems</li>
                    <li>Made an additive synthesizer for 8-bit sounds</li>
                </ul>

                <p>In my spare time, I like to noodle on the keyboard, read (especially sci-fi and history books), and play fetch with my cat.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

